FlappyCastform
===============

Flappy Castform is a Flappy Bird inspired game made using Pygame. Castform and the background will change depending on
the current weather and time in Vancouver.

Getting Started
---------------------------

These instructions will get you a copy of the project up and running on your local machine.

Prerequisites (Windows)
---------------------------

1. Must have Python 3.x installed

2. Must have Pygame installed. You can do so by pasting the following snippet into your command prompt

```
$ py -m pip install -U pygame --user
```

Installing
---------------------------

1. Clone the repository and have fun!

```
Example
```